OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA
OL,6,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,7,Ffew days with spells of rain, but some
OL,8,Fdrier and brighter periods too,
OL,9,Fespecially in the east.
